            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;in headers for sure, but what if &lt;code&gt;using namespace std&lt;/code&gt; is present only in the implementation files?&lt;/span&gt;

