              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/1084774/pskocik&quot; title=&quot;55,249 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;PSkocik&lt;/a&gt;
